      <title>受美国通胀弹性影响，金价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/gold-xauusd-resumes-gains-as-middle-east-tensions-offset-hot-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，金价大幅上涨，但被美国通胀报告打断，该报告引发了人们对美联储今年降息幅度低于预期的担忧。]]></description>
